类 Client

java.lang.Object
model.Client
所有已实现的接口:
java.lang.Cloneable
直接已知子类:
Administrator, Coach, User
public class Client
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
client model class. It represents all type of client (User, Coach and Administrator).

18 May 2021
版本:
1.4

Yubo Wu
